少 Salon 啲單剪都係幾十蚊<br />\n如果真係搵到啱自己心水嘅師傅<br />\n咪俾多十蚊 （其實都唔係貴）<br />\n咁個師傅又開心，又會可能記得你<br />\n下次飛髮可能又有得飛先，個樣又寬容啲，可能又飛得仔細啲"},{"pid":"df3064f466921f972bcfe7e1b3121a852bf9f383","tid":1253244,"uid":274883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f74471814eb117278dda9ae920045cb6ecdc2fd","tid":1253244,"uid":90807,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"真 以前去開200蚊 又要book 去到又要排隊 又要搭車<br />\n呢年全部落街50蚊速剪 咪又係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"成日驚50蚊會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19a04f7395c498dab632453cc2aa6425ed11116","tid":1253244,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}